extras.optText:
##### Instagram Get Highlights How-To 

This template lists the instagram highlights of multiple accounts, and downloads them to specified folder

Follow these steps to test this template;

**1.** Edit the Config Node.

**2.** Install Instagram package. You can examine a sample package installation from [here](https://docs.robomotion.io/getting-started/tutorials/slack-integration#adding-slack-package-to-designer)

**3.** Update msg.root_path field with the path of the folder that the highlights will be saved.

**4.** Update msg.os_splitter field  with the path splitter of your operating system. If your OS is Windows it is "\\", in Linux or MacOS it is "/"
